/**
 * Status Automation System - Advanced automation for shipment status changes
 * 
 * Features:
 * - Rule-based automation
 * - Conditional triggers
 * - Scheduled actions
 * - Event-driven automation
 * - Performance monitoring
 * - Exception handling
 */
